<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prison-n">prison <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'prɪzn/    美 /'prɪzn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>监狱；牢笼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>escape from prison</strong> 
越狱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go to / get out of prison</strong>
入 / 出狱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>put sb in / send sb to / throw sb into prison</strong>
把某人关 / 送进监狱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mandela fought for black people and was <strong>in prison</strong> for almost thirty years.
曼德拉为黑人而斗争并坐了将近三十年的牢。</p></div></div>